Sara in her cheerleader outfit



The kids came around to the department for some early trick-or-treating...Sara and Diana had made crepe paper pompoms, but Debra found these real ones she'd been given at a basketball game, and gave them to Sara.
Taken Thursday, October 31, 2002, 04:47:50pm.  Original image size: 1538x2307, 6.5Mb
Technical details: Canon EOS D60, 1/125s @ F2.8, ISO 400, 28mm/F2.8 (45mm equiv)
